Class AllListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.event.AllListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PropertyChangeListener, EventListener, ItemListener, PageableListener, TreeExpansionListener, ColumnModelListener, ListDataListener, ListSelectionListener, TableModelListener, TreeModelListener, TreeSelectionListener

    public abstract class AllListener
extends Object
implements ListDataListener, ListSelectionListener, PropertyChangeListener, TableModelListener, TreeModelListener, TreeSelectionListener, TreeExpansionListener, PageableListener, ColumnModelListener, ItemListener
    A listener that can respond to any MIWT event.
    Author:
    Pat B. Double (double@i2rd.com)
